{"tid":1849570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【豬腦抗疫】梁卓偉：世衛開8個鐘會好科學   世衛：不建議撤僑   美英歐日韓德澳：立即撤僑","createTime":"2020-01-29T06:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T06:58:29.000Z","uid":79563,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1aae47c1b8c47c020fc011c255e82b77adaab9eb","tid":1849570,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:28:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾廢物, 應立即撤佢職：<br />\n<img src=\"http://assets.wenweipo.com/image/2020/01/25/karljing_245337195513f83410fa570dc444aa72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.wenweipo.com%2Fimage%2F2020%2F01%2F25%2Fkarljing_245337195513f83410fa570dc444aa72.jpg&h=33b87cc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多國宣布將從武漢撤僑 美國及日本最快今日派包機</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505169-20200128.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505169-20200128.htm&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Js2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=25fe3643\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1505169-20200128.htm&h=9dbe96a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1505169-20200128.htm</a><br />\n內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情持續擴散，多國計劃從武漢撤僑。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府預料最快今日起派遣包機到中國武漢，接走滯留當地的日本人，正在加緊開展協調工作。美國較早前表示，將在今日以包機運送外交人員和美國僑民離開武漢。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙政府亦正與中國和歐盟合作，將撤離目前在中國武漢地區的大約20名西班牙公民。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部表示，正努力為在湖北省的英國公民提供一個離開的選擇。法國就表示，預計從當地撤離約800名法國公民中的數百人。德國外交部表示，考慮從受疫情影響的中國地區撤離德國公民。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">澳洲武漢撤僑去聖誕島隔離 距澳洲1600公里</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2550000/2551275/20200129_christmas_v1_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2550000%2F2551275%2F20200129_christmas_v1_1024.png&h=e26f6677&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8b7fc15877bc38128af179d598c2e386d46ea71","tid":1849570,"uid":22422,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"宜家美國帶頭架空世穢同世謬<br />\n大把國家跟隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb0fe08a01122428d154311d2721226ef0d8ddf","tid":1849570,"uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:31:54.000Z","msg":"梁卓偉呢D廢物, <br />\n基本上, 就係當世衛係上帝, <br />\n當世衛新聞稿係聖經<br />\n<br />\n人地西方文明國家, 係自己國民著想<br />\n係早走早著<br />\n安全第一<br />\n話知你世衛UP乜春<br />\n<br />\n世衛UP乜, 你梁卓偉就UP乜, <br />\n基本上唔駛比錢請你啦, 你可以執包伏躝啦！<br />\n去世衛搵條友嚟SIT你個位咪得囉，仲乜事要出糧比你條廢老呢？"},{"pid":"07929555a984c2e9e49c684e17712635544e0ee9","tid":1849570,"uid":329698,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"c8b7fc15877bc38128af179d598c2e386d46ea71","tid":1849570,"uid":22422,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"宜家美國帶頭架空世穢同世謬<br />\n大把國家跟隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:32:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲組織好快收皮<br />\n名存實亡"},{"pid":"0ac86a2ac61a8fde3bce258ee4b16a9c16c95f09","tid":1849570,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"c8b7fc15877bc38128af179d598c2e386d46ea71","tid":1849570,"uid":22422,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"宜家美國帶頭架空世穢同世謬<br />\n大把國家跟隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:33:01.000Z","msg":"世穢由雞珍揸旗開始, <br />\n就知仆街<br />\n<br />\n台灣入唔到世穢, 其實一D都唔可惜<br />\n<br />\nAPPLY COMMON SENSE就可以<br />\n唔需要世穢, 垃圾組織"},{"pid":"2e2cd6d94a0e0f42f7e75995b1379fdc7f1f47dc","tid":1849570,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"07929555a984c2e9e49c684e17712635544e0ee9","tid":1849570,"uid":329698,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"c8b7fc15877bc38128af179d598c2e